#
#   MIDI itself is **the universal music-technology
#   interoperability standard** ‚Äî invented in 1983 by the
#   joint effort of Roland (Ikutaro Kakehashi) + Sequential
#   Circuits (Dave Smith) + Oberheim + Yamaha + Korg + Kawai,
